# 13. Manifest Schema

Manifest is canonical JSON serialized per RFC 8785 (JCS).

Recommended top-level fields:

```json
{
  "schema_version": "1.0",
  "protocol_version": "1.0",
  "canonicalization_version": "1.0",
  "merkle_version": "1.0",
  "hash_algorithm": "sha256",
  "hash_algorithm_version": "1.0",
  "shingling_version": "1.0",
  "ocr_extraction_version": "1.0",
  "tenant_id": "...",
  "project_id": "...",
  "attestation_id": "...",
