Manifest must include:

* schema version
* protocol version
* canonicalization version
* Merkle version
* hash algorithm and version
* shingling preset/version when applicable
* extraction method metadata
* OCR engine/version/language-pack version when applicable
* leaf set references or embedded leaf metadata
* Merkle root
* desktop/device signature
* customer-managed signature if enabled
* policy context

Encoding rules:

* JSON canonicalization: **RFC 8785 (JCS)**
* JSON-embedded hashes: **lowercase hex**
